American Express Co's Shearson LehmanBrothers said it helped establish a national pooled capitalprogram offering low-cost financing to small and medium-sizedbusinesses.    Shearson said that it and non-profit &lt;American DevelopmentFinance Corp> will help organize the Enterprise Capital Fund,which will initially have a 100 mln dlr pool.    The capital will be used primarily to make loans thatfinance small business growth and other projects thatcontribute to job creation and economic develpment, Shearsonsaid. Reuter&#3;